text.paragraph:
For the primary endpoint (clinical remission at Week 6), treatment with intravenous ENTYVIO did not result in statistically significant improvement over placebo (
                                 Table 7
                                 ). Secondary endpoints including assessments at Week 10 were not tested because the primary endpoint was not statistically significant.

